text: King of Spain mainly refers to: * The monarchy of Spain, headed by the King or Queen of Spain * Felipe VI, current King of Spain * The full list of Spanish monarchs It may also refer to: * "King of Spain", a song by the Canadian band Moxy Früvous * "King of Spain", a song by the American indie rock band Galaxie 500 * "King of Spain", a song by Swedish indie folk artist The Tallest Man On Earth * Future Kings of Spain, an Irish rock band * Raoul and the Kings of Spain, an album by the English band Tears for Fears * A nickname for Ashley Giles, an English cricketer
title: King of Spain (disambiguation)
